      "translations": {
        "en.bab-ul-qaim-publications": [
          "Hadith.3825 - Al-Is ibn al-Qasim asked Abu Abdullah (as) about a slave who claimed that he was free but did not provide any evidence for his claim.\nThe Imam (as) replied: \"Yes, you may buy him.\""
